          "symWidth": 8.790570175438596,
          "text": "HMPH ,  PROTECT ?! HAVE  YOU  FORGOTTEN  THE RULES  OF  THE  HEAVENLY  MAIDEN KINGDOM ?  IN  A  DUEL  OVER  A MAN ,  LIFE  AND  DEATH  ARE UP  TO  FATE !!",
